The CZR-9001 blaster rifle was a model of blaster rifle manufactured by Czerka Corporation available during the Galactic War between the Galactic Republic and the Sith Empire. Specific blasters were often designed for specific roles in combat.
The 6-2Aug2 hunting rifle was a model of slugthrower rifle present in multiple homesteads on backwater worlds in the Outer Rim Territories such as Tatooine, Viscara, and Saleucami.
